snippet.title: DuneCrawl - Official Gameplay Overview Trailer | The MIX Fall Showcase 2024
snippet.description: Join developer Alientrap fo ra deep dive into the gameplay of DuneCrawl in this trailer for the upcoming online coop action-adventure game where players take on the roles of desert faring privateers. Together, players explore the dust seas by piloting their Dune Crawler, a gigantic walking crustacean festooned with cannons and treasure maps. DuneCrawl will be available on PC in 2025.
